rows.label: tlk44600184_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I haven't seen you around here before.
You must be new...

rows.label: tlk44600184_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm always borrowing books from the
Library Philosofia. That's not to say
I especially "like" them...

rows.label: tlk44600184_01_msg0003
rows.name:
It's just the only thing I'm able to
really do around here, what with the
cost of living these days...

rows.label: tlk44600184_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't get me wrong, I'm proud of my
country, but the outlook is so bleak,
books are my only means of escape.
